92
00:04:47,075 --> 00:04:50,450
The sum value is again going ahead and summing up the true values for

93
00:04:50,450 --> 00:04:54,145
each column to give us the total number of missing values in each column.

94
00:04:54,145 --> 00:04:59,300
Our second line of code only selects columns that have more than zero missing values and

95
00:04:59,300 --> 00:05:01,640
