00:05:57,920 --> 00:06:01,025
and you can see once we repeat the exact same code,

114
00:06:01,025 --> 00:06:05,060
that the age and body columns are no longer appearing here because there's no

115
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:09,820
longer any na values that we can see that were generated for these columns.

116
00:06:09,820 --> 00:06:12,590
Let's actually go ahead and put this all together in

