00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:17,720
Again, pulling from a short sklearn tutorial.

119
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:20,480
Pipelines are really handy way of assembling a bunch of

120
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:23,735
sklearn operations altogether and determine flow.

